  <CalDefinition Description="If TP function is activated and the actual TP station is below TP Quality Level for more than TP_LostHoldTime, the radio will look for a TP station in FM Memory which is above TP Quality Level, if no TP station is found in FM Memory start seek for a TP station in entire band which is above TP_SeekLevel, but only if radio is not the active If TP function is activated and the actual TP station is below TP Quality Level for more than TP_LostHoldTime, the radio will look for a TP station in FM Memory which is above TP Quality Level, if no TP station is found in FM Memory start seek for a TP station in entire band which is above TP_SeekLevel, but only if radio is not the active source or when volume 0 is selected." Name="TP_QualityLevel" References="GIS-338-206B TP Seek" Usage="LOW,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU">
